{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"490cc1e18f","title":"向党交心万岁","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd9e82a098","index":0,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":11,"articleId":"490cc1e18f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"26123aa5a7","name":"高崇民"},{"id":"7885f44b48","name":"民盟副主席"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"24fd3c3a51","type":"title","text":"向党交心万岁","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"1b584f680d","type":"authors","text":"民盟副主席高崇民","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"a8a350ff2e","type":"paragraph","text":"把千年来、百年来，封建的、资本主义的旧社会，改造为社会主义到共产主义的新社会，","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"244fa362c8","type":"paragraph","text":"这是历史发展的规律，决定了我们进步的人类。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"02f5ac874f","type":"paragraph","text":"这个翻天复地的革命事业，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"33a0732b16","type":"paragraph","text":"包括了由旧社会来的人们在内。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"2b89738212","type":"paragraph","text":"必须立场一致，思想一致，面向一个目标，跟着无产阶级的先锋队，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"aab43221a4","type":"paragraph","text":"从六亿人民的利益出发，有进无退。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"5df2c57e08","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，人的阶级性和习惯性总是在作祟，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"7ae547fa67","type":"paragraph","text":"因而新和旧的斗争，是无比的尖锐。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"7913d947f2","type":"paragraph","text":"对真理必须有认识，下最大决心，自我改造，才是","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"50d531bd8f","type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢、智慧。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"761496f809","type":"paragraph","text":"整个社会改造运动，不是对个人谁整谁，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"285d4054cb","type":"paragraph","text":"生产关系、经济基础都已改变了，梁上君子岂能安睡?","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"930cdfdb4f","type":"paragraph","text":"顾虑徘徊，甚或抗拒，轻则落伍，重则犯罪，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"45c9243c15","type":"paragraph","text":"现在不鼓起干劲，彻底交心，将来必贻后悔。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"14c51aea95","type":"paragraph","text":"向党交心是个人思想改造的跃进，形势迫人，不容颓废。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"c7b46c3e30","type":"paragraph","text":"目前条件和美好远景，弥足珍贵，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"5031c89fbe","type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定要改造成“俯无所怍，仰无所愧”。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"fd2c54d8d7","type":"paragraph","text":"我为人人，人人为我，永世无坠，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"276579f22c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要高呼：向党交心万岁!","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"},{"id":"d7fcb6e90f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《光明日报》1958年5月11日。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f"}],"page":{"id":"d4674c60e6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"490cc1e18f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}